OL,3,CAmazon to cut around 16,000 jobs in
OL,4,Cfresh round of layoffs
OL,6,FAmazon has told staff it plans to cut
OL,7,Fabout 16,000 jobs globally as part of
OL,8,Fefforts to streamline its operations.
OL,10,FIt is the latest major round of
OL,11,Flayoffs at the retail technology giant
OL,12,Fand comes just three months after it
OL,13,Faxed around 14,000 jobs.
OL,15,FThe majority of affected jobs will be
OL,16,Fin the US, it is understood, but the
OL,17,FUK operation will still see some jobs
OL,18,Faxed.
OL,20,FThe company did not disclose how many
OL,21,FUK workers will be affected.
