OL,3,CAmazon to cut around 16,000 jobs in
OL,4,Cfresh round of layoffs
OL,6,FBeth Galetti, senior vice president of
OL,7,Fpeople experience and technology at
OL,8,FAmazon, told staff in a blog post: "As
OL,9,FI shared in October, we've been
OL,10,Fworking to strengthen our organisation
OL,11,Fby reducing layers, increasing
OL,12,Fownership and removing bureaucracy.
OL,14,F"Some of you might ask if this is the
OL,15,Fbeginning of a new rhythm ` where we
OL,16,Fannounce broad reductions every few
OL,17,Fmonths. That's not our plan."
