OL,3,CAmazon to cut around 16,000 jobs in
OL,4,Cfresh round of layoffs
OL,6,FThe announcement, which came after
OL,7,Fredundancy plans were accidentally
OL,8,Fshared with some staff in error on
OL,9,FTuesday, comes amid a backdrop of
OL,10,Fgrowing AI adoption within corporate
OL,11,Foperations.
OL,13,FLast year, boss Andy Jassy suggested
OL,14,FAmazon was likely to reduce its staff
OL,15,Fcount over the coming years as it
OL,16,Fincreases its use of artificial
OL,17,Fintelligence for many tasks.
