OL,3,CAmazon to cut around 16,000 jobs in
OL,4,Cfresh round of layoffs
OL,6,FThe company employed around 1.57
OL,7,Fmillion at the end of September last
OL,8,Fyear, with about 350,000 of these
OL,9,Facross its corporate workforce, while
OL,10,Fthe majority of employees work in its
OL,11,Fwarehouses.
OL,13,FIt employs around 75,000 people across
OL,14,Fits operations in the UK.
OL,16,FEarlier this week, Amazon confirmed it
OL,17,Fwould close its remaining Amazon Fresh
OL,18,Fand Go retail stores across the US,
OL,19,Ffocusing instead on its Whole Foods
OL,20,Fstore business.
