OL,3,CAmazon to cut around 16,000 jobs in
OL,4,Cfresh round of layoffs
OL,6,FLast September, Amazon announced the
OL,7,Fclosure of its 19 Amazon Fresh stores
OL,8,Facross the UK, impacting around 250
OL,9,Fjobs.
OL,11,FRachel Fagan, organiser for the GMB
OL,12,Funion, said: "Amazon is showing itself
OL,13,Ffor what it is: a company that cannot
OL,14,Fbe trusted to do the right thing by
OL,15,Fworking people in the UK.
OL,17,F"Amazon overseeing thousands of job
OL,18,Flosses will cause huge damage in towns
OL,19,Fand cities across the country.
